      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCOOTIN' SCOOBY (1) hit the ground running last time with a fast early split and never headed, leading throughout to win by 5 lengths (24.87) over 431m at this track. Winner at his latest appearance in the quickest time on the card. Looks the one to beat. QUEEN GOUT (2) flew the lids with a fast early split and went on to clock 25.19 when a one length winner over 431m at this track. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in three starts. Deserves serious consideration again. GO FORWARD BLOCK (3) has a strong record this track and trip with four wins and three placings from eight starts. Placed last time (25.27) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing second and beaten one length. Can feature with the right run. FROM THE DISCO (8) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track over 431m.",
